Test Case ID: TC-007

Title:
Verify item details remain correct in cart

Priority:
Medium

Type:
Data Integrity

Preconditions:
1. User is successfully signed in.
2. User in on the Cart page with items in the cart.

Test Steps:
Check details (Verify: Product name, Price, Description, Quantity) of the items on the cart page and verify they match the details on the products page

Expected Result:
Product name, description, price, and quantity displayed in the cart exactly match the corresponding product information on the Products page.
